OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FA campaign aiming to transform
OL,7,Fpeople's attitudes towards investing
OL,8,Fhas launched, with research suggesting
OL,9,Fthat seven in 10 (69%) people rarely
OL,10,For never talk about the subject.
OL,12,FThe Invest For The Future campaign is
OL,13,Fbacked by several financial services
OL,14,Ffirms, with support from the Treasury,
OL,15,Fthe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)
OL,16,Fand the Money and Pensions Service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
