OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FA survey commissioned for the campaign
OL,7,Findicated that 44% of people with
OL,8,Fsavings but no investments ` which
OL,9,Fcould equate to 10.1 million savers
OL,10,Facross the UK ` would be interested to
OL,11,Flearn more about investing.
OL,13,FPrevious FCA research has indicated
OL,14,Fthat around seven million adults hold
OL,15,Fmore than #10,000 in cash savings and
OL,16,Fcould be missing out on the benefits
OL,17,Fof investing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FCash savings that can be easily
OL,7,Faccessed may be useful for emergencies
OL,8,Fbut those behind the campaign said
OL,9,Fexcess savings may dent people's
OL,10,Fability to achieve their long-term
OL,11,Ffinancial goals.
OL,13,FInvestments may potentially outperform
OL,14,Fcash savings over the longer term but
OL,15,Fthe value of investments can go down
OL,16,Fas well as up and people should
OL,17,Fconsider the level of risk they feel
OL,18,Fcomfortable with. People may also want
OL,19,Fto consider any fees when weighing up
OL,20,Finvestment options.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
