PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FThe campaign aims to support more
OL,7,Fpeople in viewing investing as
OL,8,Fsomething for them ` and that
OL,9,Finvesting could be a natural "next
OL,10,Fstep" from saving.
OL,12,FIt will roll out in phases, starting
OL,13,Fwith digital and social channels, and
OL,14,Fbe expanded to television from the
OL,15,Fautumn.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
