PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FThe campaign will include a character
OL,7,Fcalled "Savvy the Squirrel" and
OL,8,Finclude "savvy cabs" ` where taxi
OL,9,Fpassengers can chat with content
OL,10,Fcreators and investors about money and
OL,11,Finvesting.
OL,13,FA fleet of taxis will be transformed
OL,14,Finto "savvy cabs" in Manchester this
OL,15,Fweek, those behind the campaign said.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@[O]pD@IOUpD@TO]vD@FOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
