PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FEconomic Secretary to the Treasury
OL,7,FLucy Rigby said: "With greater
OL,8,Fawareness of the benefits of
OL,9,Finvesting, more people will be able to
OL,10,Fmake informed decisions about how to
OL,11,Fmake their savings work harder for
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"That will mean greater prosperity and
OL,15,Ffinancial resilience for households
OL,16,Facross the country and strengthened
OL,17,Fdomestic capital markets, too."
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
