PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FSasha Wiggins, chairwoman of the
OL,7,Fretail investing campaign and CEO of
OL,8,Fprivate bank and wealth management at
OL,9,FBarclays, said: "The UK has a strong
OL,10,Fsavings culture but a significant
OL,11,Finvesting gap with too many still
OL,12,Ffeeling investing is not for them."
OL,14,FChris Cummings, chief executive of the
OL,15,FInvestment Association and deputy
OL,16,Fchairman of the retail investing
OL,17,Fcampaign, said: "There is clear demand
OL,18,Ffrom millions of savers who want to do
OL,19,Fmore with their money, but do not
OL,20,Falways feel confident about where to
OL,21,Fbegin."
OL,26,@qD@QOUtD@cO]yD@QOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
