OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FRichard Flint, chief executive of
OL,7,FHargreaves Lansdown, said: "Too many
OL,8,Fpeople in Britain feel that investing
OL,9,Fisn't for them. This campaign is about
OL,10,Fbuilding confidence and awareness, so
OL,11,Fmore people feel able to take that
OL,12,Ffirst step and make their money work
OL,13,Fharder for them.
OL,15,F"People won't change their behaviour
OL,16,Fovernight but through creating an
OL,17,Fengaging and simple campaign to answer
OL,18,Fpeople's questions, we hope that a
OL,19,Ftraditionally dry subject will become
OL,20,Fmore accessible and real."
OL,26,@oD@\OUwD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
