OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FSarah Pritchard, deputy chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of the FCA, said: "We want
OL,8,Fconsumers to navigate their financial
OL,9,Flives with confidence and invest for
OL,10,Fthe future.
OL,12,F"This campaign is an important part of
OL,13,Fthat, building the stronger investment
OL,14,Fculture we need. It sits alongside our
OL,15,Ftargeted support rules which will help
OL,16,Fmillions make informed decisions about
OL,17,Ftheir finances."
OL,26,@oD@]OUtD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
