OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FChanges were made from April 6 meaning
OL,7,Fsome firms can offer targeted support
OL,8,Fto help people make better-informed
OL,9,Fdecisions about what to do with their
OL,10,Fmoney, based on what they would
OL,11,Frecommend to those in similar
OL,12,Fcircumstances.
OL,14,FTargeted support aims to fill the gap
OL,15,Fbetween people receiving general
OL,16,Fguidance and paying for individualised
OL,17,Fadvice, enabling more people to make
OL,18,Finformed decisions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FIn December, the FCA said at least 18
OL,7,Fmillion people could be offered extra
OL,8,Fhelp with their investments and
OL,9,Fpensions over the next decade with the
OL,10,Fintroduction of targeted support.
OL,12,FOpinium carried out the survey of
OL,13,F4,000 people across the UK in April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FJames Andrews, managing editor at
OL,7,FSmart Money People and Be Clever With
OL,8,FYour Cash, said: "While investing has
OL,9,Fbecome more democratised in recent
OL,10,Fyears, thanks to a wealth of digital-
OL,11,Ffirst investment solutions, ease of
OL,12,Faccess has not mitigated its inherent
OL,13,Frisks.
OL,15,F"Yes, investing offers the potential
OL,16,Ffor greater growth, but it also
OL,17,Fcarries the risk that you get back
OL,18,Fless than you put away, especially
OL,19,Fover the short term.
OL,26,@pD@ROUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,F"Britons should ensure they assess the
OL,7,Ffull range of Isas available to them
OL,8,Fand choose what best suits their
OL,9,Ffinancial situation.
OL,11,F"Both stocks and shares Isas and cash
OL,12,FIsas have their own benefits, and the
OL,13,Fright choice depends on individual
OL,14,Fgoals. Cash Isas mean you know exactly
OL,15,Fwhat you have saved and are better
OL,16,Fsuited to short-term financial goals.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,F"Stocks and shares Isas are more
OL,7,Fsuited to long-term investing, where
OL,8,Fgrowth is more likely over time,
OL,9,Fmaking them appropriate for retirement
OL,10,Fplanning or building wealth for later
OL,11,Flife."
OL,13,FFrom April 6 2027, changes will mean
OL,14,Fthat, while the total annual Isa
OL,15,Fallowance will still be #20,000,
OL,16,Fadults aged under 65 will be able to
OL,17,Fput away only up to #12,000 in a cash
OL,18,FIsa, with the remaining #8,000
OL,19,Fallowance potentially going into
OL,20,Fstocks and shares.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FSavers aged 65 and over will retain
OL,7,Fthe annual #20,000 subscription limit
OL,8,Ffor a cash Isa.
OL,10,FAndrew Prosser, head of investments at
OL,11,FInvestEngine, said: "Transparency and
OL,12,Feducation around costs must be central
OL,13,Fto any efforts to boost people's
OL,14,Fconfidence in investing."
OL,16,FHolly Mackay, chief executive at
OL,17,FBoring Money, said: "We need to take
OL,18,Finvesting out of the members' clubs
OL,19,Fand into the school run, into the pub
OL,20,Fand onto our screens."
OL,26,@sD@UOUvD@YO]yD@UOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,FShe said that targeted support "has a
OL,7,Fvital role to play in enabling
OL,8,Fmillions of cash-only savers to take
OL,9,Fthe first step into investing".
OL,11,FCaroline Raines, director of corporate
OL,12,Faffairs at Compare the Market said:
OL,13,F"With more financial content being
OL,14,Fshared online than ever before, it's
OL,15,Fvital that we ensure consumers are
OL,16,Fsignposted to accurate, balanced
OL,17,Fguidance rather than misleading
OL,18,Finformation.
OL,26,@nD@`OUqD@^O]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776906184
OL,3,CIndustry-backed campaign aims to boost
OL,4,CUK's investment culture
OL,6,F"Credible voices in the creator space
OL,7,Fhave an important role to play here `
OL,8,Fhelping to translate complex topics
OL,9,Finto everyday language without
OL,10,Fdownplaying the risks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]
